## Import



IAM OpenID Connect Providers can be imported using the `arn`, e.g.,

```sh
 $ pulumi import aws:iam/openIdConnectProvider:OpenIdConnectProvider default arn:aws:iam::123456789012:oidc-provider/accounts.google.com
```
